, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=May 21, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| June 6}}\n| ''[[Just as I Am (Brantley Gilbert album)|Just as I Am]]''\n| {{sortname|Brantley|Gilbert}}\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-06-06/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for June 6, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=May 28, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| June 13}}\n| ''[[Jekyll + Hyde]]''\n|{{sort|Brown Zac|[[Zac Brown Band]]}}\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-06-13/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for June 13, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=June 4, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| June 20}}\n| ''[[Django & Jimmie]]''\n| {{sortname|Willie|Nelson}} and [[Merle Haggard]]\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-06-20/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for June 20, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=June 11, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| June 27}}\n| ''Now That's What I Call Country Volume 8''\n| Various Artists\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-06-27/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for June 27, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=June 18, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| July 4}}\n| ''[[Jekyll + Hyde]]''\n| {{sort|Brown Zac|[[Zac Brown Band]]}}\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-07-04/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for July 4, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=June 25, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts| July 11}}\n| ''[[Pageant Material]]''\n| {{sortname|Kacey|Musgraves}}\n\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2015-07-11/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for July 11, 2015|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=July 2, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row